              <td style="padding: 1.2rem; text-align: center; color: #0f0; font-weight: bold;">6-10 settimane</td>
              <td style="padding: 1.2rem; text-align: center; color: #0f0;">1-2 settimane</td>
              <td style="padding: 1.2rem; text-align: center; color: #f00;">6-18 mesi</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #333;">
              <td style="padding: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">🔌 Integrazioni</td>
