            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #333; background: #0a0a0a;">
              <td style="padding: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">📱 Mobile Responsive</td>
              <td style="padding: 1.2rem; text-align: center; color: #0f0; font-weight: bold;">✅ Garantito</td>
