                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" style="background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 1.5rem;">
                  💻 Quali tecnologie usi per sviluppare il gestionale?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
